  • Deprecated Annotation Type Elements 
    Annotation Type Element and Description
    com.google.errorprone.BugPattern.category
    This category field hasn't provided much value, as the 'problem domain' of each BugChecker is evident from the checker itself. We've introduced BugPattern.tags() as a means to apply general tags to checks.
